  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA88">
<l>nāṭilu niṉṉaṭiyē nāṭuva ṉāṭōṟum</l>
<l>pāṭilu niṉpukaḻē pāṭuvaṉ – cūṭilum</l>
<l>poṉṉāḻi yēntiṉāṉ poṉṉaṭiyē cūṭuvēṟ</l>
<l>keṉṉāki leṉṉē yeṉakku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I search, I search your feet. When daily</l>
<l>I sing, I sing your praise. To me who, if I wear [anything],</l>
<l>wear the gold[-ringed] feet of him who raised the golden discus,</l>
<l>if anything should happen to me, what [of it]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
